'''[[spectral]] [[line]]'''
#{{physics}} a dark or bright line in an otherwise continuous [[spectrum]] caused by the [[absorption]] or [[emission]] of light, at a single [[wavelength]], by the movement of [[electron]]s between [[energy level]]s of an [[atom]] or [[molecule]]

